# VibeCraft — Orc Horde Fighter (Grunt)
#
# Body composition: ORC GRUNT (Orc Horde faction)
#
# Orc diet & lifestyle (informing muscle/fat distribution):
#   Raw meat, ale, gruel + raiding/brawling/heavy labor lifestyle
#   → heavy muscle mass, thick subcutaneous fat layer, barrel torso
#   → bull neck, tree-trunk limbs, broad heavy jaw, forward-leaning posture
#   → explosive strength from constant physical conflict
#
# Orc proportions: ~6.5 heads tall (shorter/stockier than human 7.5)
#   Barrel torso: waist ~90% of chest width (vs human V-taper ~63%)
#   Bull neck: thick and short, supporting heavy skull
#   Broad jaw, heavy brow ridge
#   Tree-trunk limbs: uniformly thick with heavy muscle and fat
#
# Anatomical basis: Gray's Anatomy layers (bone→muscle→fat→skin)
#   still apply but with orc-proportional thickness at every joint
# Body mesh: single connected component, no disjoint parts
# Armor: separate overlay plates over continuous body form
#
# 1139 vertices, 2016 triangles
# Convention: Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
